This is Args version 1.0.0.

Args is a small C++ library for parsing command line arguments.


COMPILING ARGS

Just run build.rb which is a Ruby program and a project file.


REQUIREMENTS

For compiling Args you should have installed:
 * Ruby programming language (http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/)
 * mxx_ru Ruby gem (http://rubyforge.org/projects/mxx-ru/)
